summary: reblog if you love dan and phil
title: reblog if you love dan and phil
body:
BUT WAIT! THERE’S MORE!

Reblog if you -

  • respect Dan and Phil’s privacy
  • respect that they both have a personal life
  • respect that they are both individual people
  • respect that they have other friends, who may be female
  • would never ask them about their sexuality
  • would never ask them about Phan
  • would never ask them about any romantic relationships, past or present
  • would never ask them about any theories
  • would never try to find their address
  • would never leak their address, if you accidentally found out
  • would never go to their address if it was accidentally leaked

But those are the basic things which I hope all of you would follow.

Here are some harder ones. Reblog if -

  • you know what a joke is and will never take those theories seriously if explicitly stated
  • you know what a joke is, and what crosses the line
  • you would not hate on anybody who makes those theories
  • you respect everyone and know that not everyone will ship what you ship and that that is okay
  • respect that (if you don’t ship Phan) that other people have opinions, and that you can keep yours, as long as you do not spread hate
  • you would not hate on any fan account.
  • you would not hate on any other fandom
  • you would not hate on any other unassuming YouTuber (unless they are an actual asshole)
  • you would not hate on any younger members of the Phandom
  • you would not condescend upon any younger members of the Phandom
  • you will not act superior towards newer members of the Phandom
  • you would welcome any Phandom members with welcoming arms

Also, reblog if -

  • you would never cause drama
  • you would never diagnose Dan and Phil (particularly Dan) anything, even if you just mean well
  • you will not spam any other comment sections
  • you will not shout at anybody spamming the comment sections, and maybe tell them to stop, POLITELY
  • you would never force anyone to love Dan and Phil because we all have different opinions
  • you are aware that other people have different opinions and that if it does not harm anyone, then that is okay.
  • you would not hate on fanart or fanfiction.
  • you would not hate on NSFW fanart or fanfiction
  • you would not hate on self-insert fanfictions or imagines (unless it is honestly really, really bad, and then you can just laugh at it)
  • you would not insult any other Phandom member, because you don’t know them

Finally, reblog if -

  • you will not bug them if they split up (Brendon Urie fans, you know what I’m talking about)
  • you will not spread hate if they quit YouTube, or if one of them quits YouTube
  • you will not threaten them if they quit YouTube, or if one of them quits YouTube
  • you will just support the other Phandom members if they split up
  • you will not blame the Phandom if they split up
  • respect that they are both human people with human people lives
  • respect that they have both grown as people and that they are different people than what they were a few years back
  • you will never use their past against them
  • you will always love/respect Dan and Phil, even if they stopped posting videos.
  • you will always love/respect Dan and Phil, even if you have grown past them.
  • you will always love/respect Dan and Phil, even if they or one of them dies
  • (however, if for some reasons they really mess up and do something really disrespectful, then you will not support them)
  • you will always be a part of the Phandom if you don’t want to leave
  • you are free to leave the Phandom any time you wish.
  • you will always be welcome in the Phandom any time you wish
  • you just want to spread love.

Hopefully, people reblog this, or this will be embarrassing. Feel free to add more if I missed any!
